    "Furthermore, the hybrid architecture that integrates LLM reasoning with traditional detectors achieves the best trade-off between accuracy and reliability, reaching an F1-score of 97.2% and demonstrating its effectiveness in simulation-based power system scenarios.",
    "Future work will extend this framework to larger-scale power systems, incorporate temporal and multimodal inputs, and assess LLM robustness under dynamic operating conditions.Table II.",
